## üèóÔ∏è Architecture

**Layered Design**
```
CLI Layer ‚Üí Services ‚Üí Models ‚Üí Connection Layer
```

**Key Components**: Telegram processing ‚Ä¢ Real-time Conbus communication ‚Ä¢ HomeKit bridge ‚Ä¢ Multiple XP server support ‚Ä¢ Configuration management

